data.description: The Texana plan is a two-story home featuring 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and 2 car garage The gourmet kitchen includes granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and open concept floorplan with the kitchen opening to the dining room and family room. The master suite features an attractive master bath with optional separate tub and shower and large walk-in closet. The entry boasts a large open study. Upstairs you'll find a game room and open to below floorplan built standard.
